title: Li'l Abner
description:
I noticed that, while there are soundtracks for most popular musicals here, I couldn't find one for Li'l Abner, so I tracked one down and uploaded it myself.
This is my first upload, so if I made any mistakes, please don't hold it against me.

I'm going to try to seed for 48 hours, but that may not be possible, so if someone could help me seed ASAP, that would be great.
